postMessage:
Team roles manager installed!

Usage:
import { TeamRoles } from '@/components/auth-team-roles/team-roles'

<TeamRoles
  members={members}
  pendingInvites={invites}
  currentUserId="user-1"
  onRoleChange={async (memberId, newRole) => { /* update role via API */ }}
  onRemoveMember={async (memberId) => { /* remove member via API */ }}
  onInvite={() => router.push('/invite')}
  onResendInvite={async (inviteId) => { /* resend invite email */ }}
  onCancelInvite={async (inviteId) => { /* cancel pending invite */ }}
/>

Requires shadcn/ui: npx shadcn@latest add button card badge
